text: Kampos () is a former community in the Karditsa regional unit, Thessaly, Greece. Since the 2011 local government reform it is part of Karditsa.Kallikratis law Greece Ministry of Interior Population 5,469 (2001). The seat of the community was in Stavros. ==References== Category:Settlements in Greece Category:2011 disestablishments in Europe
title: Kampos, Karditsa
